        "comment": "The pinterest itself is wonderful. But the app seems to be a knife to cut a tree. The main purpose of the app is to view images. But you cannot zoom enough to read the contents of the images. Also the full screen mode is not very straightforward which it should have been. When you are in full screen mode, most of the screen is occupied the visual search option and there is no way getting rid of it. In a single word you just cannot view the images properly with this app. I think for this reason it would be fair enough to say this app has failed to pursue it's primary goal.",
